  "instruction": "Write an HTML5 section labeled with aria-labelledby pointing to its h2 heading. The section contains one explanatory paragraph.",
  "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <title>Labeled section</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <section aria-labelledby=\"billing-heading\">\n      <h2 id=\"billing-heading\">Billing cycle</h2>\n      <p>Invoices are generated on the first day of each month.</p>\n    </section>\n  </body>\n</html>",
